=== Key API Discoveries (not documented in AGENTS.md) ===

1. service_runtime_from_env() 
   - Exists in generate-lib/src/runtime.rs
   - Reads env var → connects → ensure_schema → registers everything
   - NOT mentioned in generated AGENTS.md (old version)

2. GraphNode.id() returns Option<&Value>
   - Must use .and_then(|v| v.try_u64()) to get u64
   - After update save, returns 0 (upstream quirk)

3. update_*() methods return &mut Self
   - Must separate from save() call
   - entity.update_name(...) → .audit_as("...").save(&ctx)
